Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到換班時間了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候多時了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一目標 鎮壓完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是相當無趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「那個」聖地的警備嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.88,0:02:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是警備 不如說是用來監視牽制他國的擺設吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且換崗人員的生活設施 全都在聖地裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說只要潛入了內部 其餘的就是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來這應該是最困難的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉喲 第二、第三目標也鎮壓完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此下去 不就可以把全部的警備所都鎮壓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也可以 但聖機師為數不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這麼多繭也沒用處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且被修利馮注意到就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的警備是完全獨立的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來愛美拉去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種幫不上忙 又囉哩囉唆的人不在不是更好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去解決我的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔的走狗竟擅自使喚別人的屬下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不曉禮數呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 那還真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你這 看來很順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四、第五、第六目標 鎮壓完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 你就在一旁好好看著吧

Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(960,720)}襲  來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於今日的來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人衷心致謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想並非空談
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動必得實施
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不失其意義
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位的各項努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將引領我們通往新生紀元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望諸位謹記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久後我軍主力就會到達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位出發吧 讓此刻成為我們慶祝勝利的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警備所被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得多賺點印象分才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利利索索地一個個收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們知道我們的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西會有用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 如果離開水線會變回繭的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪音？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯特雷尤正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸後的濃煙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是警備所那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警備所？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼警報沒有拉響
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地警備所 已排除近七成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 很不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是讓聖地由我支配而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯特雷尤的旗艦要塞！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個控制室也由我掌控了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部乖乖投降的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 那老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是這邊 修利馮的聖機人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？藏了兩台啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來解決 其他的交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 中央控制室被佔領了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅斯特家的小鬼也擺出一幅自大的拽樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 知道了 馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為佔領了那裡就能支配一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人笑掉大牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那面具女說的風暴難道是指這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈止是風暴 簡直是颱風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的巴巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎樣讓巴比倫穿過那麼狹窄的溪谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夏拉殿下 學院長來電聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先能簡潔說明一下目前所發生的狀況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也應該瞭解我在斯特雷尤的處境吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對天地神明發誓 這件事跟我毫無關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的情況必須讓全校人員去避難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能提供協助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用說嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學院長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 白鳥城立刻準備出發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去協助引導學生避難和抵禦敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖地的教職人員已開始進行避難引導了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今闖入聖地的可是斯特雷尤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在此時不做點事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的立場就很不利了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家的訓示是自己的事情自己做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你即使不肯替我出這個頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就權作是報答那些平日對你愛護有加的人也行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻就去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我走著瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱雅 你也跟劍士一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然襲擊我們的是斯特雷尤…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是達古麥亞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夏拉殿下請盡快…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱雅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想和他一起的話 那就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是避難
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七目標已攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經足夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面差不多也亂作一團了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微去整點兒零用錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦烏 瓦烏 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是外面好像很混亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個借我用用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？先別著急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的武器馬上就裝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台足矣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東西裝太多會影響機動力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據小嵐的情報 這裡好像是聖機工的工房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒值錢的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦烏 這傢伙的反應變得更靈活了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來這些不都是之前偷襲療養地的山賊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦烏 這倆傢伙交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～啊 等等 劍士 你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧拉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑精靈的負面時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常比起來真像完全變了個人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著這麼害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會對你很溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:10:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳東西 那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你在抓著哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂動啊 要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宰了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點 就夠著…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都讓你看到我不成體統的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒受傷就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負面時間真是可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再抱久一點也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是大好時機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個趕緊去確認是否有沒來得及避難的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！電燈泡馬上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍士閣下 公主就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 請一定努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倆傢伙 我要扣他們薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 實戰起來貌似也沒什麼了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 真卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍伊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是反抗我們的下場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑精靈領域很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡快解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙沒有武裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防衛機能啟動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們去確保避難學生的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦外各處中彈 但損傷輕微
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人炮台陸續出現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑他們已經做的很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓聖機人全體出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓這些傢伙妨礙巴比倫的前進路線
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴巴隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈伯尼亞的芙羅拉女皇傳來通信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴巴隆卿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對聖地進行軍事侵犯 到底有何目的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來此處的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了又能怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想阻止我的話 就用實力來說話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓我感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在聖地開戰 若沒有一些大義作口實可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴巴隆大人 前方有巨大的物體靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮門展開完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射擊開始～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 真是好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是華麗的登場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也能接收避難學員與教職人員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請將通道打開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幫了大忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 小心聖機人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊 請快些！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 好危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗緹亞會長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗緹亞會長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很危險 請別這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為大家爭取點避難時間 我還能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方數量太懸殊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 學生會長想登上聖機人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 會長大人也想跟我們玩玩麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微嚇嚇她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:16:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗緹亞會長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個卑鄙小人 難道不覺得羞恥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許用那種臭屁的口氣跟我們說話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉碧絲快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 我要保護麗緹亞會長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈 自己找死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是劍士 那個礙眼的侍從
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 拉碧絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 麗緹亞會長沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 快起來 抓住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了 拉碧絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會痛扁他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧拉殿下 這台機工人交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡 野生動物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙落荒而逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥技場的防禦體系相當健全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖機人越不過埃納的水線 這裡很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各班長確認人員的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:19:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1班到4班從地下16號通道搭乘教會戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5班到8班從29號通道前往拉夏拉殿下的白鳥城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9班以後從7號通道進入芙羅拉殿下的裝甲列車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚各自去向就開始行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那按照學號排列好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛麗姆跟普露是8 伊麗絲拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的吧 達古麥亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道總有一天會變成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亞老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是拉夏拉殿下的護衛騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他是梅斯特家族的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亞老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各班級全部到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家按順序兵分三路經地下通道避難了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個也快去避難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍士？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想幹什麼啊 那個白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被大家稍微捧高些就自以為了不起似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但畢竟只是個侍從
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈能與我們男聖機師相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 打中了 打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本區域沒落下什麼人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人真夠嗆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聖地開著裝甲列車和巨型戰艦火拚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是前所未聞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達古麥亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是 劍士？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他究竟想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 那傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:21:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍士同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學員和職員總計1149人 均於白鳥城得到妥善保護
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.42,0:22:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人員健康狀態良好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負傷者也僅為輕傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.39,0:22:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若就此讓兩人一同見鬼去就謝天謝地了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩方都活力十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:22:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:22:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然都怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:22:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.95,0:23:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍士先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.54,0:23:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夏拉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 那是光之屬性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.08,0:23:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光之屬性？×2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教會秘藏的古代文獻中曾提到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.84,0:23:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為光所籠罩之人拯救世界 為暗所籠罩之人毀滅世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:23:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為暗…所籠罩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.61,0:24:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是光與暗表裡一體
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光或許會轉為暗 反之亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.36,0:24:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是白色的聖機人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.33,0:24:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.81,0:24:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那時的聖機人駕駛員是劍士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.36,0:24:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖機師？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.04,0:24:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是我們的劍士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.84,0:24:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 才一轉眼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.81,0:24:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊 誰來救救我啊啊啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.72,0:25:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不要背對著那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.96,0:25:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 從我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.27,0:25:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.93,0:25:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達古麥亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.74,0:25:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.21,0:25:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦烏安麗 去掩護他
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.84,0:25:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒那個空閒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.47,0:25:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨 正中下懷 收拾掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.79,0:26:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 在那裡面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.86,0:26:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一對一倒也罷了 敵人若以眾欺寡的話可十分不利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.33,0:26:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是被石柱和埃納水線環繞的牢籠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.42,0:26:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.48,0:26:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.18,0:26:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亞姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.41,0:26:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這林立的石柱裡 機動性無法得到發揮
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.96,0:26:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.43,0:26:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.47,0:26:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.26,0:26:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從左右迂迴包抄
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.78,0:26:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.58,0:27:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往你的方向去了 科露蒂涅
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.41,0:27:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 來吧 老娘會好好疼愛你的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.05,0:27:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在這裡起跳
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.40,0:27:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.84,0:27:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.96,0:27:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.83,0:27:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊？那個聖機人的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.32,0:27:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒見過純白的聖機人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.34,0:28:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.17,0:28:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是我們的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.95,0:28:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柾木劍士同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.39,0:28:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 劍士同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.99,0:28:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夏拉殿下隨從的那位？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.56,0:28:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是聖機師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.02,0:28:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上繭時 是我親眼所見的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.66,0:28:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那白色聖機人是劍士在駕駛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.37,0:28:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 劍士小弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.89,0:28:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.30,0:28:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是劍士同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.27,0:28:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個柾木劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.21,0:28:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.09,0:28:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在林立的石柱與水線的環繞下戰鬥極為困難
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.46,0:28:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.39,0:28:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真有那麼難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.69,0:28:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傻小子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.32,0:28:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.29,0:28:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖有眾多已至達人境界的聖機師們在此鬥技場中戰鬥過
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.81,0:28:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還沒有誰能完成那樣的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.03,0:28:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超乎想像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.66,0:28:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.35,0:29:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達古麥亞 此時應選擇暫時撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.22,0:29:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說什麼 怎能因為那傢伙而退兵
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.42,0:29:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.64,0:29:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.92,0:29:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克裡夫
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.16,0:29:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.28,0:29:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒是我們自投羅網 被誘入了他的狩獵場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.92,0:30:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后大人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.83,0:30:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 雪音妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.91,0:30:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你保護瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.58,0:30:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈敢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.44,0:30:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來吃驚的事還真多
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.15,0:30:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到劍士是聖機師
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.40,0:30:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.34,0:30:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.32,0:30:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還擁有那麼強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.46,0:30:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次可要找拉夏拉好好地詢問詳情才行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.41,0:30:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.51,0:30:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了劍士 敵人的聖機人近乎全軍覆沒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.47,0:30:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應可迫使斯特雷尤就此撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.16,0:30:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真不好說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.63,0:30:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.65,0:30:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎還備有後手呢 巴巴隆卿
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.44,0:30:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.99,0:30:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴比倫 到達目標
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.80,0:30:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦身控制 誤差修正
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.79,0:31:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界確認 構造檢查 掃瞄開始
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.69,0:31:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反結界陣 開始構築
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.65,0:31:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.07,0:31:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道巴巴隆的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.01,0:31:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.26,0:31:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.00,0:31:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達古麥亞
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.63,0:31:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.61,0:31:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 科露蒂涅還…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.31,0:31:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽的話她自己會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.08,0:32:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這種怪物我能有什麼辦法啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.64,0:32:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 梅塞亞姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.51,0:32:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我的聲音難道你聽不見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.40,0:32:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.24,0:32:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了 凱亞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.76,0:32:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.59,0:32:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.89,0:32:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快你就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.06,0:32:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.96,0:32:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖機神的台座…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.10,0:32:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亞姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.88,0:32:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.06,0:32:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界解析完成 開始侵入
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.75,0:33:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.25,0:33:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.90,0:33:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 覺醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.82,0:33:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.22,0:33:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱亞 梅塞亞其實並非你的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.44,0:33:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亞是你父親在遺跡中與聖機神一同被發掘出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.60,0:33:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先史文明所創造出來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.80,0:33:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.49,0:33:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不信就看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.49,0:33:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.14,0:34:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多…露…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.12,0:34:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.16,0:34:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.60,0:34:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接通教皇大人的直通專線
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.71,0:34:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟有此事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.34,0:34:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬分之一機率的事態被觸發了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.81,0:34:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴虐之神復活的時候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.62,0:34:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.01,0:35:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快帶領大家去避難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.95,0:35:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想讓她們陪葬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.94,0:35:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 梅塞亞姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.79,0:35:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.05,0:35:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.83,0:35:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.54,0:35:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 僅靠聖機人有這能耐 當真了得
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.09,0:35:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很危險 快去避難
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.90,0:36:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做好最後的確認後也會離開
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.66,0:36:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能留下你在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.63,0:36:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能丟下那個傻小子和姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.69,0:36:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你一定要平安歸來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.94,0:36:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 這樣就結束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.97,0:36:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔？怎麼了？攻擊啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.30,0:36:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼對劍士下不了手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.79,0:36:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受梅塞亞的人格影響？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.99,0:36:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.32,0:36:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我不能拒絕命令
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.60,0:36:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.83,0:36:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,細胞組織的劣化似乎比預想的還要糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.08,0:36:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱雅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.08,0:36:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有落單的學生了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.59,0:36:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也差不多該去避難了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.09,0:36:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是劍士先生還…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.35,0:36:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經沒什麼能做的了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.62,0:37:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擾敵之類的工作還能做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.25,0:37:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 被對方當成目標會很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.70,0:37:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我們很可能會拖劍士的後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.41,0:37:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退吧 那白癡的話沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.21,0:37:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.02,0:37:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.68,0:37:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒吧 梅塞亞姐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.50,0:37:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.09,0:37:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亞跟我已經融合了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.12,0:37:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我記得 在這裡和你一同經歷過的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.50,0:37:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五花八門的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.60,0:37:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 請你把那些忘掉 那我就感激不盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.94,0:37:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然的確是很愉快的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.02,0:37:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已無法繼續待在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.06,0:37:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 劍士 能到我的身邊來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.33,0:37:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡沒有我的容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.94,0:37:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒是多露 來我們這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.58,0:38:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的容身之所我會幫你開拓的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.28,0:38:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.72,0:38:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.58,0:38:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥才是我存在的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.63,0:38:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為此而被製造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.61,0:38:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣就滿足了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.73,0:38:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.11,0:38:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.94,0:38:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學院長 已確認全部學生避難完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.17,0:38:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那麼準備出發
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.53,0:38:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.97,0:38:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您沒事嗎 奧拉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.21,0:38:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損害狀況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.59,0:38:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了劍士 全都獲救了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.43,0:38:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那麼立刻出航
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.57,0:38:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙羅拉殿下 來列車避難的學生已全部收容完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.82,0:38:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖有數人受傷 但221人均平安抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.33,0:38:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.32,0:39:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮發射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.56,0:39:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后大人 劍士先生還在戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.33,0:39:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 但應該不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.78,0:39:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 雪音妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.86,0:39:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮發射準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.85,0:39:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員撤退完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.10,0:39:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮車輛撤退到安全區域
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.62,0:39:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮發射後讓前方車輛自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.95,0:39:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切順利的話應該能阻止敵人追擊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.76,0:39:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亞姐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.57,0:39:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.97,0:39:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.79,0:39:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.18,0:39:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我母后現在要做蠢事了 請迴避！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.15,0:39:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.18,0:40:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.28,0:40:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.40,0:40:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亞姐
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.02,0:40:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是無計可施啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.08,0:40:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想奪回聖地 我們連像樣的戰鬥力都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.40,0:40:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼去結界工房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.73,0:40:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.67,0:40:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果萬一聖機神啟動的話 就來我這裡 」
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.99,0:40:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏奈瓦師傅這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.87,0:40:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.49,0:41:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍霍
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.73,0:41:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多該把你知道的全都說出來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.15,0:41:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 但是在那裡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.59,0:41:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍士 去迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.49,0:41:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.24,0:41:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織嚴重劣化 劍士的力量太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.52,0:41:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還能戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.86,0:41:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連變型都沒戲了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.04,0:41:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.77,0:41:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.91,0:41:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.72,0:41:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙羅拉你個大姨媽
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.28,0:41:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個沒常識的中年女人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.35,0:41:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把我們都捲進去的話可怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.03,0:41:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正得救了 就隨她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.87,0:41:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果OK怎樣都行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.67,0:42:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.18,0:42:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易收集的水晶全都落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.40,0:42:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～費了好大的功夫的說…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.89,0:42:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.95,0:42:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的確已約法三章不許再挖水晶的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.78,0:42:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這事 必須給我老實交代！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.45,0:42:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.79,0:42:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒危機感的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.95,0:42:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達古麥亞 作戰算是成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.29,0:42:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無須如此沮喪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.62,0:42:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.38,0:42:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太勉強自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.62,0:42:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次我可不一定在你身邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.94,0:43:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.90,0:43:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟預期一樣在潛伏中
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.55,0:43:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的準備也很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.58,0:43:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.83,0:45:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為惹麻煩的只有巴巴隆而已
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.40,0:45:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 先去奧拉的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.49,0:45:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 異世界的聖機師物語
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.73,0:45:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「思緒」
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.75,0:45:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要清算那筆舊帳